little-kid character falling in love with a bewitching beauty on a
trapeze.
   It was the 1,874th star dedicated in the Walk of Fame along
Hollywood Boulevard and Vine Street. Paramount Pictures, sponsor of
the curbside honor, paid $3,500 for the Herman star.
