<TEXT>
   A truck speeding in the wrong lane
slammed into a passenger bus and sent it crashing into another
truck, killing 12 people and seriously injuring 19, officials said.
   The truck burst into flames on impact in Wednesday's crash on
the Mexico-City-Veracruz highway near this city in Veracruz state,
